text: Okay as a token, but awesome as the start of an avalanche.
The Dissident Anglo-Protestant diaspora is only very crudely summarized as 'American.'
Ankle-biting nobodies of the day are undergoing precipitous quality decline.
First Ozzy Osborne, then Hulk Hogan -- everywhere darkness and wailings of grief.
... History will recall this moment as a great culling of the gods.
